      "content": "Your feelings of exhaustion and hopelessness are incredibly heavy, but please know that what you are experiencing right now does not define your entire story. Struggling with these thoughts of being a burden is a sign of deep pain, not a truth, and reaching out to a crisis counselor at [988](https://www.988lifeline.org/) can help you navigate through this darkest moment without having to carry it alone.",
      "source": "target",
